.IPs "avi\ \ "
Audio Video Interleave file
.IPs "wav\ \ "
Waveform Audio
.IPs "swf\ \ "
Macromedia Flash
.IPs "flv\ \ "
Macromedia Flash video files
.IPs "rm\ \ \ "
RealAudio and RealVideo
.IPs "au\ \ \ "
